title: The whisper of the winds carries
description: The whisper of the winds carries a new challenge, seeker. There exists a place, an untamed stretch known as Mucky Duck, where the earth itself holds secrets. Its rugged terrain and muddy depths are a proving ground. You are tasked to journey into the heart of Mucky Duck and, amidst its treacherous paths, obtain 500 pennies. They are not merely coins, but a key to what lies hidden within the mire. Return when your pockets are heavy with the metallic weight of your success.

trailLocation.title: Mucky Duck
trailLocation.description: An exciting off-road trail perfect for ATV, 4x4, and dirt bike adventures through rugged terrain.
